# Quick Start

### 1. Initialize the library
```javascript
await ZYNQ.init();
```

### 2. Get the full list of games
```javascript
console.log(ZYNQ.list);
```

### 3. Get a random game (any)
```javascript
const game = ZYNQ.random().list[0];
console.log(game.name);
```

### 4. Get a random game (shortcut)
```javascript
const game = ZYNQ.getRandomOne();
console.log(game.name);
```
